channel.itunes:author: Pastor Paul Artino
channel.itunes:subtitle: 7ten is a young adults ministry
channel.itunes:summary: A gathering of young adults that desire an environment where the Gospel is celebrated, lived out and taken out. we long to be an authentic and passionate community; one that desires to be a part of God's work of restoration and healing to hurting and questioning. we deeply desire to take the remedy (Jesus) to the many social and spiritual ills that plague our city and beyond. we believe that God's Word is the solution and by proclaiming and living the Gospel we will have a significant influence in our world.
